<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LOTO6 蛻・梵繝励Λ繝・ヨ繝輔か繝ｼ繝 V3</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="loto6_fabilogo.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&family=Outfit:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://html2canvas.hertzen.com/dist/html2canvas.min.js"></script>
    <style>
        :root {
            --sidebar-bg: #0f172a;
            --main-bg: #f8fafc;
            --accent-blue: #38bdf8;
            --accent-green: #22c55e;
            --accent-orange: #f59e0b;
            --text-dark: #1e293b;
            --text-muted: #64748b;
        }

        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background-color: var(--main-bg); color: var(--text-dark); margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }
        .page-wrapper { display: flex; min-height: 100vh; }
        .sidebar { width: 260px; background: #ffffff; color: var(--text-dark); padding: 15px; position: sticky; top: 0; height: 100vh; overflow-y: auto; border-right: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .main-content { flex: 1; padding: 15px; min-width: 0; }

        .card { background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); margin-bottom: 20px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }

        /* 繧ｳ繝ｳ繝医Ο繝ｼ繝ｫ */
        
        .sidebar { width: 260px; background: #fff; border-right: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding: 20px 15px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow-y: auto; transition: 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1); flex-shrink: 0; }
        .sidebar.hidden { margin-left: -290px; opacity: 0; pointer-events: none; }
        
        .top-layout { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow-y: auto; background: #f1f5f9; }
        .top-header { background: white; padding: 15px 30px; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 15px; }
        .top-header h1 { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; color: #1e3a8a; margin: 0; line-height: 1; }
        .btn-toggle { background: transparent; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; border-radius: 4px; padding: 6px 10px; cursor: pointer; color: #475569; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; transition: 0.2s; }
        
        .content-wrapper { max-width: 1600px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; padding: 20px 15px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20px; }

        .main-controls-wrapper { padding: 25px; background: #fff; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 0px; max-width: 1400px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; }
        .notice-box { background: #f9f9f9; border: 1px solid transparent; border-left: 4px solid #aaa; border-radius: 6px; padding: 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        
        .controls-flex { display: flex; gap: 15px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; background: #fff; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        
        .btn { padding: 12px 24px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 8px; cursor: pointer; border: none; transition: 0.2s; color: white; display: inline-flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 5px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); }
        .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); }
        
        .predict-btn { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1fa331 0%, #157321 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(21, 115, 33, 0.3); }
        .eliminate-btn { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6c757d 0%, #495057 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(108, 117, 125, 0.3); }
        .river-btn { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2196F3 0%, #0d47a1 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.3); }
        .river-btn.active { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9800 0%, #e65100 100%); box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(255, 152, 0, 0.3); border: 2px solid #fff; }

        input[type="number"], select { width: 60px; padding: 6px; border: 1px solid #aaa; border-radius: 4px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box; }

        /* 繝・・繝悶Ν (loto6_board.html縺ｫ蜷医ｏ縺帙◆繝・じ繧､繝ｳ) */
        .board-container { background: #f1f5f9; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; flex: none; box-shadow: none; display: flex; justify-content: center; max-width: 1540px; margin: 0 auto; width: 100%; }
        table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; text-align: center; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
        th, td { border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; padding: 2px 1px; font-size: 11px; }
        th { background-color: #ccddec; position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 10; font-weight: bold; color: #2e3e59; padding: 4px 1px; transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s; }
        
        .id-col { background-color: #e8eef1 !important; width: 54px; min-width: 54px; position: sticky; left: 0; z-index: 11; font-weight: bold; color: #2e3e59; padding: 2px 0; }
        th.id-col { z-index: 12; background-color: #b3cdd9 !important; }
        .sb-col { display: none !important; }

        .num-cell, .header-num { width: 22px; height: 22px; border-radius: 3px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #fff; font-size: 12px; font-weight: bold; box-sizing: border-box; }
        .header-num { color: #334155; background: transparent; }
        
        td { background: #ffffff; cursor: cell; transition: 0.1s; }
        td:hover { background: #f8fafc; }
        
        /* 繝懊・繝翫せ謨ｰ蟄暦ｼ夐ｻ呈棧繝ｻ逋ｽ閭梧勹繝ｻ鮟呈枚蟄暦ｼ域怙蜆ｪ蜈茨ｼ・*/
        .num-cell.bonus-cell { background-color: #ffffff !important; color: #000000 !important; border: 2px solid #000 !important; }

        /* 譛ｬ謨ｰ蟄励き繝ｩ繝ｼ繧ｯ繝ｩ繧ｹ */
        .col-1 { background-color: #1a9c2a !important; color: #fff !important; } 
        .col-2 { background-color: #00d0e0 !important; color: #fff !important; } 
        .col-3 { background-color: #f79c11 !important; color: #fff !important; }
        .col-4 { background-color: #8c8c11 !important; color: #fff !important; } 
        .col-5 { background-color: #11d911 !important; color: #fff !important; } 
        .col-6 { background-color: #fce803 !important; color: #000 !important; }
        .col-7 { background-color: #881c88 !important; color: #fff !important; } 
        .col-8 { background-color: #198080 !important; color: #fff !important; } 
        .col-9 { background-color: #1133e6 !important; color: #fff !important; }
        .col-0 { background-color: #828282 !important; color: #fff !important; }

        /* 髯､螟悶・繝・ム繝ｼ: header-num隕∫ｴ縺ｫ蟇ｾ縺励※ﾃ励ｒ縺九・縺帙ｋ */
        th.eliminated-header .header-num { position: relative; }
        th.eliminated-header .header-num::after { content: "ﾃ・; color: rgba(239, 68, 68, 1); font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; position: absolute; top: 48%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); pointer-events: none; line-height: 1; z-index: 50; text-shadow: 0 0 2px white; }

        .info-panel { padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px; display: none; }
        
        /* 莠域ｸｬ邨先棡縺ｮ螟ｧ縺阪↑陦ｨ遉ｺ逕ｨ */
        .prediction-result-display { display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; margin-top: 20px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f7ff; border-radius: 12px; border: 1px dashed var(--accent-blue); }
        .result-ball { width: 45px; height: 45px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 800; box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2); text-shadow: 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.3); }

        /* 繝励Λ繧､繝舌す繝ｼ繝昴Μ繧ｷ繝ｼ蟆ら畑繧ｹ繧ｿ繧､繝ｫ */
        .pp-footer { margin-top: 40px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .pp-link { color: #64748b; text-decoration: none; font-size: 13px; transition: 0.2s; cursor: pointer; }
        .pp-link:hover { color: var(--accent-blue); text-decoration: underline; }

        .pp-modal-overlay { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.6); backdrop-filter: blur(4px); -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(4px); display: none; align-items: center; justify-content: center; z-index: 9999; padding: 20px; }
        .pp-modal-content { background: white; width: 100%; max-width: 600px; max-height: 80vh; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; animation: pp-modal-in 0.3s ease-out; }
        @keyframes pp-modal-in { from { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; } to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; } }
        .pp-modal-header { padding: 20px 25px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
        .pp-modal-header h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-dark); font-weight: 700; }
        .pp-close { background: #f1f5f9; border: none; width: 32px; height: 32px; border-radius: 50%; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: #64748b; font-size: 20px; transition: 0.2s; }
        .pp-close:hover { background: #e2e8f0; color: #1e293b; }
        .pp-body { padding: 25px; overflow-y: auto; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; color: #475569; }
        .pp-body h3 { font-size: 16px; color: var(--text-dark); margin: 20px 0 10px; }
        .pp-body p { margin: 0 0 15px; }

        /* Searchable History & Stats */
        .history-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 10px; table-layout: fixed; }
        .history-table th { background: #f1f5f9; color: #475569; font-size: 12px; padding: 10px; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; }
        .history-table td { padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; font-size: 13px; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; }
        .history-ball-row { display: flex; gap: 4px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
        .history-ball { width: 24px; height: 24px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; color: white; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; }
        .search-wrapper { display: flex; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 15px; align-items: center; }
        .search-input { flex: 1; padding: 10px 15px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; font-size: 14px; outline: none; transition: 0.2s; }
        .search-input:focus { border-color: var(--accent-blue); box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1); }
        .capture-btn { background: #6366f1; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: none; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
        .capture-btn:hover { background: #4f46e5; }

        /* --- History Modal Styles --- */
        .modal-overlay { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(5px); display: none; align-items: center; justify-content: center; z-index: 10000; padding: 20px; }
        .modal-content { background: white; width: 100%; max-width: 800px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; animation: modal-in 0.3s ease-out; }
        @keyframes modal-in { from { transform: translateY(20px); opacity: 0; } to { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 1; } }
        .modal-header { padding: 20px 25px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; background: #fff; }
        .modal-header h2 { margin: 0; font-size: 18px; color: var(--text-dark); font-weight: 700; }
        .modal-body { padding: 20px; overflow-y: auto; max-height: 60vh; }
        .modal-footer { padding: 15px 20px; border-top: 1px solid #f1f5f9; display: flex; gap: 10px; justify-content: flex-end; background: #f8fafc; }
        
        .history-list-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
        .history-list-table th, .history-list-table td { padding: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f5f9; text-align: center; }
        .history-list-table th { background: #f8fafc; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; font-weight: 600; }
        .history-list-table tr:hover { background: #fcfdfe; }

        .btn-modal { padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 600; cursor: pointer; font-size: 13px; border: none; transition: 0.2s; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; }
        .btn-delete-all { background: #fee2e2; color: #dc2626; }
        .btn-delete-all:hover { background: #fecaca; }
        .btn-delete-selected { background: #f1f5f9; color: #475569; border: 1px solid #cbd5e1; }
        .btn-delete-selected:hover { background: #e2e8f0; }
        .btn-ticket { background: #4f46e5; color: white; }
        .btn-ticket:hover { background: #4338ca; }

        /* --- Ticket Template Styles --- */
        #ticket-template {
            position: fixed; left: -9999px; top: -9999px;
            width: 500px; padding: 20px; background: white;
            font-family: "MS UI Gothic", "MS Gothic", sans-serif;
            color: #000;
        }
        .ticket-border { border: 4px double #1133e6; padding: 15px; background: white; position: relative; }
        .ticket-title { text-align: center; color: #1133e6; font-size: 32px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .ticket-subtitle { text-align: center; color: #1133e6; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 15px; border-bottom: 2px solid #1133e6; padding-bottom: 5px; }
        .ticket-info { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .ticket-patterns { border-top: 1px solid #1133e6; padding-top: 10px; }
        .pattern-row { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #1133e6; }
        .pattern-label { width: 30px; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; color: #1133e6; }
        .pattern-nums { display: flex; gap: 12px; flex: 1; justify-content: flex-start; margin-left: 20px; font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; }
        .ticket-footer { margin-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-weight: bold; }
        .ticket-amount { font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 5px; }
        .ticket-deadline { background: #1133e6; color: white; padding: 5px 15px; border-radius: 20px; display: inline-block; margin: 15px 0; font-size: 16px; }
        .ticket-warning { color: #f00; font-size: 11px; text-align: center; margin-top: 10px; line-height: 1.5; border-top: 1px dashed #f00; padding-top: 5px; }
        .ticket-stamp {
            position: absolute; right: 20px; bottom: 40px;
            width: 80px; height: 80px; border: 2px solid rgba(255,0,0,0.7);
            border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            color: rgba(255,0,0,0.7); font-size: 12px; text-align: center;
            transform: rotate(-15deg); font-weight: bold;
        }
        .trend-accordion {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border: 1px solid #ffe082;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: #fffdf5;
        }
        .trend-header {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            background: #fff9e6;
            color: #5c4d04;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }
        .trend-header:hover {
            background: #fff2cc;
        }
        .trend-content {
            padding: 12px 15px;
            border-top: 1px solid #ffe082;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #5c4d04;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        /* --- 繝倥ャ繝繝ｼ謨ｰ蟄励・繧ｹ繧ｿ繧､繝ｫ --- */
        .header-num {
            transition: all 0.2s;
            user-select: none;
            padding: 2px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        #mainTable.manual-mode .header-num {
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        #mainTable.manual-mode .header-num:hover {
            background: rgba(31, 163, 49, 0.2);
            color: #166534;
        }

        /* 譌｢蟄倥・latestTrendBox縺ｮ蛟句挨繧ｹ繧ｿ繧､繝ｫ繧剃ｸ頑嶌縺阪☆繧九◆繧∽ｸ驛ｨ蜑企勁繝ｻ隱ｿ謨ｴ */
        .page-footer {
            margin-top: auto;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #94a3b8;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            background: #fff;
        }
        .sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 6px; }
        .sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #f1f5f9; }
        .sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #cbd5e1; border-radius: 10px; }
        .sidebar::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover { background: #94a3b8; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page-wrapper">
        <aside class="sidebar" id="sidebar">
            <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <img src="logo_loto6pro.png" alt="LOTO6 PRO" style="width: 220px; height: auto; display: inline-block; vertical-align: middle;">
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 25px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px;">
                <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="openPP()" style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent-blue); text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;">
                    孱・・繝励Λ繧､繝舌す繝ｼ繝昴Μ繧ｷ繝ｼ
                </a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="openTerms()" style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--accent-blue); text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;">
                    笞厄ｸ・蛻ｩ逕ｨ隕冗ｴ・
                </a>
            </div>

            <div style="font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 18px; color: #1e293b; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 8px; font-weight: bold;">投 邨ｱ險医ョ繝ｼ繧ｿ</div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #1e293b;">譛ｬ譌･縺ｮ繧｢繧ｯ繧ｻ繧ｹ</div>
                <div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;" id="statVisitors">***</div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 12px;">
                <div style="font-size: 13px; color: #1e293b;">迴ｾ蝨ｨ髢ｲ隕ｧ謨ｰ</div>
                <div style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;" id="statViewing">***</div>
            </div>
            <div style="font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 25px; color: #1e293b; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 8px;">
                谺｡蝗槭∪縺ｧ縺ｮ邱丈ｺ域Φ螳溯｡梧焚<br>
                <span id="statPredictions" style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold;">***</span>
            </div>

            <!-- 繧ｵ繧､繝峨ヰ繝ｼ・壽怙譁ｰ蠖馴∈螳溽ｸｾ繧ｻ繧ｯ繧ｷ繝ｧ繝ｳ (閾ｪ蜍墓峩譁ｰ蟇ｾ雎｡) -->
            <div id="latestWinnerStats" style="margin-bottom: 25px;">
                <div style="font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1e293b; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 8px; font-weight: bold;">腸 譛譁ｰ蠖馴∈螳溽ｸｾ</div>
                <div id="winnerNumbersInfo" style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.7; color: #1e293b;">
                    <strong>隨ｬ2092蝗・莠域ｸｬ螳溯｡梧焚 (0蜿｣)</strong><br>
                    <div style="display:flex; gap:4px; margin: 8px 0; justify-content: flex-start; flex-wrap: wrap;">
                        <span class="history-ball" style="background:#198080;">8</span>
                        <span class="history-ball" style="background:#f79c11;">13</span>
                        <span class="history-ball" style="background:#881c88;">27</span>
                        <span class="history-ball" style="background:#fce803; color:#000;">36</span>
                        <span class="history-ball" style="background:#881c88;">37</span>
                        <span class="history-ball" style="background:#f79c11;">43</span>
                        <span class="history-ball" style="background:#ffffff; color:#000; border:2px solid #000; width: 22px; height: 22px; font-size: 10px;">3</span>
                    </div>
                    1遲・ 0蜿｣ / 2遲・ 0蜿｣<br>3遲・ 0蜿｣ / 4遲・ 0蜿｣<br>5遲・ 0蜿｣<br>
                    <span style='color:#ef4444; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold;'>繧ｭ繝｣繝ｪ繝ｼ: 480,712,171蜀・/span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div style="font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #1e293b; border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 8px; font-weight: bold;">焚・・縺ｿ繧薙↑縺ｮ莠域Φ繝ｻ讀懃ｴ｢螻･豁ｴ</div>
            <div id="predictionHistory" style="padding-right: 2px; margin-bottom: 20px;"></div>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 15px; border-top: 1px dashed #e2e8f0; padding-bottom: 50px;">
                <a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="openContact()" style="font-size: 13px; color: #1e293b; text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-weight: 600;">
                    笨会ｸ・縺雁撫縺・粋繧上○
                </a>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <section class="top-layout">
            <div class="top-header">
                <h1>
